{"tid":1145875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那事業淨營收下滑 家樂福傳考慮退出支那市場","createTime":"2019-05-09T01:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T08:43:03.000Z","uid":32511,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a867b509ebd43127a4e50c81a6efa8c50a74e19","tid":1145875,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"彭博資訊引述知情人士報導，法國零售巨擘家樂福正在考慮出售中國事業，可能成為近年來又一家決定退出這個國家的國際性消費品廠商。<br />\n <br />\n彭博報導，家樂福正在與一名顧問共同合作，已經開始尋找潛在買家。該公司出售中國事業可能開價10億美元，不過最後也可能選擇只出售部分股權，或甚至決定不出售，目前家樂福尚未做出最終決定。<br />\n <br />\n家樂福發言人則表示，出售中國事業「並不在議程上」。<br />\n <br />\n彭博報導表示，家樂福此舉將加入其他跨國民生消費產品業者調整中國事業的行列。愈來愈多消費者在網路上購物，已使這個全球第二大經濟體的零售業日漸失色。上周有消息來源透露，德國零售業者麥德龍集團（Metro AG）已出售其中國事業的大多數股權。<br />\n <br />\n據家樂福年度財報，去年中國事業的淨營收下滑約10%至36億歐元。"},{"pid":"2dffb3947d7a6b7fc496c6fcee9ff2144c885905","tid":1145875,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"個個去幫襯大潤發，華潤萬家啦，駛鬼幫襯你外資公司咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548789d5e85223a4e0dd065cd245a4de80719390","tid":1145875,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"家樂福好似好摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c8c1dcef36cb8982440c63cbe57089db4f8ba2","tid":1145875,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-08/carrefour-is-said-to-weigh-options-for-china-including-sale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-05-08%2Fcarrefour-is-said-to-weigh-options-for-china-including-sale&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfnG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=07d58689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-08/carrefour-is-sai